---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { info } from "../data/info";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <header class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="space-y-4 order-2 sm:order-1">
        <h1
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent"
        >
          About
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text dark:text-dk-text/80 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>{info.name}</strong> is a
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_engineering"
          >
            full-stack engineer</a
          >
          with a background in
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_intelligence"
          >
            business intelligence</a
          >
          and
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economics"
          >
            economics</a
          >. This website is primarily dedicated to Nick's <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/music">music</a
            > and <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/posts">his blog</a
            >. 
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 sm:order-2 shrink-0">
        <Image
          src={info.picture}
          alt={info.picture_alt}
          width={96}
          height={96}
          class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full object-cover grayscale contrast-115 shadow-sm border border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10"
        />
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-6 mt-6 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        About Nick
      </h2>

      <p>
        His professional journey began in academia, producing a
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="/posts/making-nuclear-energy-competitve-with-fossil-fuels-and-natural-gas"
          >report</a
        >
        for the
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://ners.engin.umich.edu/"
          >University of Michigan's NERS department</a
        >
        on the economics of nuclear reactors in the United States.
      </p>

      <p>
        After that, Nick worked for one
        of Michigan's premier economic development firms, <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://rightplace.org">The Right Place, Inc</a
        >, providing the public with economic
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://www.rightplace.org/news/west-michigan-businesses-plan-to-increase-wages-between-3-2-to-4-6-in-2023"
          >reports</a
        >
        and helping kickstart key
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://rightplace.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/production/uploads/downloads/public-resources/State-of-the-Region-2022_FINAL.pdf"
          >regional data reports</a
        >. His data, charts, and analysis were featured in the
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://www.wzzm13.com/article/money/economy/the-right-place-sees-positive-future-for-west-michigan-at-economic-outlook-presentation/69-cdbf79c8-3edc-4ae9-a642-8c4dea266d69"
          >news</a
        >
        alongside Michigan's top economic leaders.
      </p>

      <p>
        His work evolved into software engineering, leading to the creation of
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://luniv.tech">Luniv Technology</a
        >, a small software shop Nick founded where he provides custom software, websites, and business intelligence to local businesses.
      </p>

      <p>
        Nick holds a bachelor's degree in  
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Economics">economics</a> 
          and
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Philosophy">philosophy</a>. His
        work primarily focuses on
        <strong>.NET/C# and TypeScript/JavaScript.</strong> Nick also frequently assists on projects regarding <strong>custom APIs, Python, CRMs, ERPs, SQL Server, PostgresSQL, and SQLite.</strong>
      </p>

      <section class="pt-6">
        <h2
          class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4"
        >
          Personal Interests
        </h2>

        <ul
          class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text/80 dark:text-dk-text/80"
        >
          <li>Writing on <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/posts">his blog</a
            > 📝
          </li>
          <li>Producing <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/music">music</a
            > through <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/posts/switching-back-to-fl-studio">FL Studio</a
            > and hardware like MIDIs/drum machines
          </li>
          <li>Hanging out with his dog and best friend,
            <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/bruce-the-dog">Bruce</a
            > 🐕
          </li>
          <li>Reading books 📚</li>
          <li>Cooking! 🍳</li>
          <li>Exercising, hiking, and running races 🏃‍♂️</li>
          <li>Traveling, especially around the United States - see his trips to
            <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/posts/chicago">Chicago</a
            >
            and
            <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="/posts/houston">Houston</a
            > ✈️
          </li>
          <li>Exploring trends in technology, business, and economics 📈</li>
          <li>Video games, mainly FPS like
            <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="https://dayz.com/">DayZ</a
            >
            and
            <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="https://www.counter-strike.net/">Counter Strike</a
            > 🎮
          </li>
          <li>Football, the good kind ⚽</li>
          <li>
              <a
              class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
              href="https://github.com/Sieep-Coding?tab=repositories&q=&type=&language=&sort=stargazers">Experimenting</a> with new programming languages 🛠️
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <section class="pt-6">
      <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        About this site
      </h1>

      <ul
        class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text/80 dark:text-dk-text/80"
      >
        <li>
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="/">nickstambaugh.dev</a
          >
          was hand-coded and built using
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a
          >
          for structure,
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://reactjs.org/">React</a
          >
          and
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript"
            >JavaScript</a
          >
          for interactivity,
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://www.typescriptlang.org/">TypeScript</a
          >
          for type safety, and styled with
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind CSS</a
          >. Blogging is written in
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/">Markdown</a
          >.
        </li>

        <li>
          The code is hosted on
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://github.com/sieep-coding/sieep-coding.github.io"
            >GitHub</a
          >
          and deployed via
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a
          >.
        </li>

        <li>
          This site contains no advertisements. If you want to show some love,
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/nickstambaugh"
            >buy Nick a coffee</a
          > ☕
        </li>

        <li>
          There are multiple backups of this site on
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://nickstambaugh.vercel.app/">Vercel</a
          >
          and
          <a
            class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
            href="https://sieep-coding.github.io/">GitHub</a
          >.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="pt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
        Subscribe to the blog
      </h2>
      <p>Before social media, people followed writers through RSS, and you can still do the same by subscribing to my
        <a
          class="text-inherit underline decoration-text/60 hover:decoration-text dark:decoration-dk-text/40 dark:hover:decoration-dk-text transition-colors"
          href="/rss.xml">RSS</a
        > feed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="text-sm text-text/60 hover:text-secondary dark:hover:text-dk-accent transition-colors"
      >
        ← Back to home
      </a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
